Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.90,0:00:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掌上的微风
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.73,0:00:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在光芒中一闪一闪地舞动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.44,0:00:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经能用全新的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.42,0:00:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向陌生人道早安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.19,0:00:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管回忆溢满心头
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.90,0:00:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的朝气绝不认输
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.67,0:00:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓在干掉的泪痕中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.04,0:00:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一扇通往梦想的门
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.15,0:01:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果烦恼就无法前进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.25,0:01:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.75,0:01:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会以迎接朋友的方式\N温柔地微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.19,0:01:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.86,0:01:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无意间悲伤虽然涌上心头
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.23,0:01:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会试着与人和好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.77,0:01:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这是我们的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.50,0:01:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.14,0:01:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.81,0:01:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你金榜题名
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.52,0:01:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个送给你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.96,0:01:58.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.83,0:02:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了大学之后请穿穿看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.50,0:02:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.95,0:02:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.66,0:02:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.29,0:03:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#05响子焦虑不安!五代离家出走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.30,0:03:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代还没回来吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.14,0:03:21.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经一个礼拜了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.34,0:03:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为现在是落榜通知的季节嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.88,0:03:28.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你们老是欺负他的关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.55,0:03:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们才没有欺负他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.58,0:03:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是实话实说罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.29,0:03:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这明明就是在欺负他嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.26,0:03:41.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过真叫人担心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.09,0:03:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟在这种时期…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.73,0:03:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等他全都落榜以后\N就会回来了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.70,0:03:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你这样好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.14,0:03:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.11,0:03:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总不能这样一直逃避吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.31,0:04:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是没考上一所大学\N我就回不了一刻馆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.45,0:04:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说你打算在我那里\N赖到明年吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.35,0:04:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.35,0:04:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,你看那个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.16,0:04:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中了!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.66,0:04:17.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天晚上来开烧肉派对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.50,0:04:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁跟你吃烧肉啊\N内裤比较重要,内裤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.43,0:04:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内裤?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.40,0:04:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来开烧肉派对啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.84,0:04:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行,我要买新的内裤来穿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.81,0:04:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我问你\N你现在寄住在谁的家里啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.95,0:04:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.12,0:04:42.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借我一条内裤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.32,0:04:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种东西怎么可以借人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.39,0:04:50.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些东西是我赢来的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.16,0:04:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猪头,要内裤回家拿不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.37,0:05:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钥匙…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.71,0:05:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没带
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.77,0:06:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.90,0:06:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像玩得很开心嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.80,0:06:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是新的游戏吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.94,0:06:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦,内…内裤…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.18,0:06:46.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.95,0:06:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四…四谷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.89,0:06:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重考生莫名坠楼死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.72,0:07:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疑似受不了联考之苦而自杀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.53,0:07:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了,好像不是五代
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.67,0:07:09.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过他也太过份了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.93,0:07:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要外宿的话\N至少也打通电话来不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.90,0:07:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.00,0:07:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.54,0:07:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎,这个怎么来的?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.33,0:08:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(投币式自助洗衣店)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.97,0:08:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好冷喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.11,0:08:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来我要用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.78,0:09:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.88,0:09:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没穿内裤对不对?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.90,0:09:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个老太婆真夸张\N这已经是第五盒了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.73,0:09:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,五代?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.44,0:10:02.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你是五代吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.68,0:10:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在搞什么啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.65,0:10:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家担心到连饭都吃不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.16,0:10:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之快点回来吧\N大家都在等你喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.20,0:10:28.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问,你是五代吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.20,0:10:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.93,0:11:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你是?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.83,0:11:34.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是一刻馆的?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.23,0:11:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是五代的?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.54,0:11:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢招待,吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.61,0:11:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的孙子平时承蒙你照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.98,0:11:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里,别这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.68,0:11:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才常常受到五代的照顾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.68,0:11:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…是我孙子受你照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.35,0:11:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…是我受五代的照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.09,0:11:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么这么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.69,0:11:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你实在太客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.29,0:12:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,老太婆,碗公
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.73,0:12:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.13,0:12:09.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思\N让你提这么重的行李
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.03,0:12:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别客气
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.87,0:12:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为裕作会来接我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.74,0:12:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕作?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.97,0:12:16.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我孙子的名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.81,0:12:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重考生的?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.38,0:12:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.81,0:12:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了,我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.82,0:12:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来他的名字不叫重考生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.38,0:12:27.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.39,0:12:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个小鬼也真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.32,0:12:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两三天前信就应该已经寄到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.16,0:12:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他居然没有来接我\N搞什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.26,0:12:40.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两三天前\N他怎么可能看得到明信片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.55,0:12:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.52,0:12:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.45,0:13:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再让我住几天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.35,0:13:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是无所谓啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.55,0:13:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你这样好吗?\N什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.99,0:13:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少要跟管理员连络一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.19,0:13:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要跟我提到她!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.73,0:13:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经习惯\N被朱美跟四谷他们嘲笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.54,0:13:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…可是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.37,0:13:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到管理员同情怜悯的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.61,0:13:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很难受
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.71,0:13:29.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这实在太惨了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.58,0:13:33.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,很惨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.12,0:13:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是惨兮兮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.99,0:13:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惨到谷底了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.53,0:13:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要重复说啦\N这样会觉得越来越惨的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.31,0:13:59.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.75,0:14:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走…走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.95,0:14:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代找到了没?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.42,0:14:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.39,0:14:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是五代的奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.66,0:14:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你用不着这么大声\N我听得到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.53,0:14:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也进来喝杯咖啡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.43,0:14:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.24,0:14:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我请客
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.94,0:14:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱美,过来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.65,0:14:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上就去,请你先进去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.62,0:14:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真的是五代的奶奶?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.99,0:14:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.22,0:14:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以请暂时不要在她面前\N提起五代的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.76,0:14:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道她迟早会知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.83,0:14:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我不想让\N刚到这里没多久的奶奶担心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.47,0:14:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就会穿帮的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.00,0:15:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,只要天黑之前\N把他找回来就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.61,0:15:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想说的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.84,0:15:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请节哀顺变
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.12,0:15:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕作全部都落榜了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.99,0:15:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只是时间的问题…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.49,0:15:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以,这一个礼拜…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.96,0:15:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四谷!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.23,0:15:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好啊,管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.60,0:15:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.97,0:15:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是多此一举
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.01,0:15:38.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.31,0:15:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,把她弄哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.46,0:15:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.93,0:15:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.43,0:15:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他逃走了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.40,0:16:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙会做什么事\N我大概心里有数
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.24,0:16:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙没什么毅力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.91,0:16:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.87,0:16:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他只是装得很烦恼的样子而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.61,0:16:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.01,0:16:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶都这么说了,错不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.32,0:16:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我又没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.05,0:16:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.49,0:16:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一刻馆的房客太冷漠了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.56,0:16:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,担心五代的\N只有管理员一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.16,0:16:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.33,0:16:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系,他说的是实话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.93,0:16:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你们话中带刺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.57,0:16:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶,你打算怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.37,0:16:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代不在这里的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.08,0:16:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候放榜?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.55,0:16:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天是最后一所私立大学放榜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.02,0:16:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国立大学早就放榜了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.25,0:16:57.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国立的根本考不上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.82,0:17:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天的放榜是关键
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.09,0:17:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.76,0:17:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果明天也落榜的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.93,0:17:11.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就把裕作带回去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.74,0:17:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是当然的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.27,0:17:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是那种有钱人家\N可以养光吃白饭的重考生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.91,0:17:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后没有消遣对象了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.10,0:17:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思,还让你陪我来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.24,0:17:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说,希望他能考上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.78,0:17:59.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想看到孙子哭丧的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.89,0:18:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了…\N好棒喔…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.44,0:18:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样?奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.62,0:18:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶,到底怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.89,0:18:45.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.96,0:18:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.57,0:18:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.57,0:18:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.64,0:18:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.31,0:18:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕作的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.61,0:18:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.51,0:19:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道他的准考证号码
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.06,0:19:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇,人山人海
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.56,0:19:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样什么都看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.83,0:19:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等人潮退了再来看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.90,0:19:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋,我没有那么悠哉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.20,0:19:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶,有没有看到?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.34,0:19:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起喔\N裕作应该会来看榜才对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.44,0:19:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.65,0:19:36.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上去罗,五代\N好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.12,0:19:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好,阪本,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.22,0:19:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少废话,快点看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.70,0:19:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,五代,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.96,0:19:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕作!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.87,0:19:56.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追啊,快追!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.30,0:19:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.47,0:20:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.51,0:20:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.11,0:20:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.08,0:20:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.32,0:20:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个笨蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.16,0:20:22.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶和管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.76,0:20:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是,为什么奶奶会在这里?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.90,0:20:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.87,0:20:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底有没有考上?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.77,0:20:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说啊说啊,到底有没有考上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.74,0:20:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没看啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.34,0:20:40.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个没出息的家伙\N到底在搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.68,0:20:43.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要打我啦\N头壳会被你打坏的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.35,0:20:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少废话!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.91,0:20:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.62,0:20:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人潮好像少了点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.75,0:20:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.15,0:20:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.29,0:21:27.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考上了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.16,0:21:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考上了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.21,0:21:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.62,0:21:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈,不要跳了啦,太丢脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.35,0:22:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶,不要跳了啦,太丢脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.73,0:22:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全跟不上他们的步调
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.13,0:22:06.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚大概会被他们牵着走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.46,0:22:07.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.70,0:22:13.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这样也很好啊\N有人让我们继续消遣下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.17,0:22:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为五代是我的玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.61,0:22:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来,大家请尽量喝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.61,0:22:22.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天特别宽待
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.01,0:22:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.38,0:22:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.99,0:22:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要干什么?\N放开我!放开我!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.73,0:22:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.33,0:22:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.67,0:22:44.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.74,0:22:47.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.94,0:22:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经洗干净了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.11,0:22:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.68,0:22:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么东西?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.45,0:23:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊对啊,什么东西?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.02,0:23:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.15,0:23:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕作,你又干了什么好事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.19,0:23:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶,你误会了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.32,0:23:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.96,0:23:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么到底是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.63,0:23:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不是你们想像的那种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.30,0:23:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们想像的是什么东西?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.80,0:23:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.57,0:23:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝吧,管理员,喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.27,0:23:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就尽情地喝吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.87,0:23:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶,喝个痛快,喝个痛快
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.28,0:23:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.15,0:23:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.57,0:23:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代考上了大学\N一刻馆的春天也终于到了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.81,0:23:59.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过樱花的季节\N对我来说是很难受的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.24,0:24:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回\N‘春天的冲击!响子的秘密!’
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.28,0:24:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.72,0:24:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,这个下个礼拜再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.07,0:24:35.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何你能如此若无其事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.38,0:24:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光只是眨个眼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.52,0:24:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能让我悸动不已
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.42,0:24:50.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使我身陷险境
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.66,0:24:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明已经可以相爱
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.20,0:25:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏偏时机还不成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.64,0:25:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我快要忍受不了\N快要变成了愚蠢的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.19,0:25:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是痛苦的折磨

